{"tid":1092573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打睇到fb夾公仔群嘅‘3粒糖事件’？","createTime":"2019-04-05T02:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T13:12:18.000Z","uid":8836,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e5aa8da13d85930225f7550397213ef8e5a98fd9","tid":1092573,"uid":8836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T02:56:25.000Z","msg":"首先利申左先，我只係一個普通夾友同花生友，尋晚見有人喺fb夾公仔群提起，所以即刻去睇下。。<br />\n<br />\n事源有人係一間位於荃灣嘅夾公仔機鋪因爲抽獎抽唔中得三粒糖而發爛咋，追擊左間野嘅專頁幾日，仲痴線到屌人地啲客再cap圖去自己嘅page度公審<br />\n<br />\n而發展到尋晚就有夾友忍唔住同個條友嘈，其間條友更揚言會用一萬蚊買哂部機嘅抽獎包即場開，但之後又私底下inbox比店主，結果間野嘅店主公開左對話內容，內容中個個人多次話今日下午會搵人去間鋪頭，店主都驚有人會搞事<br />\n<br />\n最後我就想係度問下有無荃灣嘅巴打去過呢間野夾過，想知究竟係有人輸唔起發爛咋咁肉酸吖定個度啲機真係咁伏呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a4e29cff13cbcf991736cee0fa70320f38e74a","tid":1092573,"uid":8836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:12:21.000Z","msg":"事源<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xeWfkj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xeWfkj.png&h=a45ff9d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ETyjXyF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETyjXyF.png&h=36a3753c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfUGrr0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfUGrr0.png&h=b2df7a8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3egxx61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3egxx61.png&h=05b1ad02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9790c7bfa43bfef12dea76d4ccd8f048f9c8444f","tid":1092573,"uid":8836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"追擊啲客<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSznVme.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail